<style type="text/css" title="charsheet">.charsheet {
    background-color: #888888;
    border: 2px solid black;
    color:black;
    width: 840px;
}

.charsheet .dummy{
	
}



.charsheet input[type=number]::-webkit-inner-spin-button,.charsheet input[type=number]::-webkit-outer-spin-button { 
  -webkit-appearance: none; 
  margin: 0;
  background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
}

.charsheet select {

<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_general" type="text/html">
<$ if(this.playerid == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
<div class='message general you' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>'>
<$ } else { $>
<div class='message general' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>'>
<$ } $>
<$ if(this.showname) { $>
<div class='spacer'></div>
<div class='avatar' aria-hidden='true'>
<$ if(this.avatar) { $><$ if(this.avatar.includes("med.webm")) { $><img src='<$!this.avatar.replace("med.webm", "frame.png")$>' /><$ } else { $><img src='<$!this.avatar$>' /><$ } $><$ } $></div><span class='tstamp' aria-hidden='true'><$!this.timestamp$></span><span class='by'><$!this.who$>:</span><$ } $>
<$=d20ext.dice_formatter.replaceInlineRolls(this.content, this, d20ext.utils.htmlAllowed + "<a>")$>
<$ if(window.is_gm) { $>
<div id="menu<$!this.id$>" class="flyout"/>
<$ } $>
</div>
</script>
<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_advancedroll" type="text/html">
<$ if(this.playerid == window.currentPlayer.id && this.characterId) { $>
<div data-characterid='<$!this.characterId$>' class='message general you' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>'  data-advancedrollid='<$!this.messageId$>'>
<$ } else if(this.characterId) { $>
<div data-characterid='<$!this.characterId$>' class='message general' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>' data-advancedrollid='<$!this.messageId$>'>
<$ } else { $>
<div class='message general' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>' data-advancedrollid='<$!this.messageId$>'>
<$ } $>
<$ if(this.showname) { $>
<div class='spacer'></div>
<div class='avatar' aria-hidden='true'>
<$ if(this.avatar) { $><$ if(this.avatar.includes("med.webm")) { $><img src='<$!this.avatar.replace("med.webm", "frame.png")$>' /><$ } else { $><img src='<$!this.avatar$>' /><$ } $><$ } $></div><span class='tstamp' aria-hidden='true'><$!this.timestamp$></span><span class='by'><$!this.who$>:</span><$ } $>
<$= this.content $>
<$ if(window.is_gm) { $>
<div id="menu<$!this.id$>" class="flyout"/>
<$ } $>
</div>
</script>
<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_advancedroll_whispersent" type="text/html">
<div class='message private whisper' data-characterid='<$!this.characterId$>' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>'>
<div class='spacer'></div>
<div class='avatar' aria-hidden='true'><$ if(this.avatar) { $><img src='<$!this.avatar$>' /><$ } $></div>
<span class='tstamp' aria-hidden='true'><$!this.timestamp$></span>
<span class='by'>(To <$!this.targetName$>):</span> <$= this.content $>
<$ if(window.is_gm) { $>
<div id="menu<$!this.id$>" class="flyout"/>
<$ } $>
</div>
</script>
<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_advancedroll_whisperreceived" type="text/html">
<div class='message private whisper' data-characterid='<$!this.characterId$>' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>'>

<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_rollresult" type="text/html">
<$ if(this.type == 'gmrollresult') { $>
<div class='message rollresult private'>
<$ } else if(this.playerid == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
<div class='message rollresult you'>
<$ } else { $>
<div class='message rollresult'>
<$ } $>
<$ if(this.showname) { $><div class='spacer'></div><span class='tstamp' aria-hidden='true'><$!this.timestamp$></span><span class='by'><$!this.who$>:</span><$ } $>
<$ var s = (this.content + "").split("|"); $>
<div class='formula' style='margin-bottom: 3px;'>
<$ if(this.type == 'gmrollresult') { $>

<$ } $>
rolling <$! s[0] $>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
<div class='formula'>
<$= d20ext.utils.strip_tags(d20ext.dice_formatter.oldformat(s[1]), d20ext.utils.htmlAllowed) $>
</div>
<strong>
=
</strong>
<div class='rolled'>
<$! s[2] $>
</div>
<$ if(window.is_gm) { $>
<div id="menu<$!this.id$>" class="flyout"/>
<$ } $>
</div>
</script>
<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_newroll" type="text/html">

<div class='message rollresult data-messageid='<$!this.id$>'>

<$ } else if(this.playerid == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
<div class='message rollresult you player-<$!this.playerid$> <$ if(this.passedSignature) { $>quantumRoll<$ } $> discord-<$! window.padrino_env || "production" $>' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>' data-playerid='<$!this.playerid$>'>
<$ } else { $>
<div class='message rollresult player-<$!this.playerid$> <$ if(this.passedSignature) { $>quantumRoll<$ } $> discord-<$! window.padrino_env || "production" $>' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>' data-playerid='<$!this.playerid$>'>
<$ } $>
<$ if(this.showname) { $><div class='spacer'></div><div class='avatar' aria-hidden='true'><$ if(this.avatar) { $><img src='<$!this.avatar$>' /><$ } $></div><span class='tstamp' aria-hidden='true'><$!this.timestamp$></span><span class='by'><$!this.who$>:</span><$ } $>

<div class='clear'></div>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
<strong>
=
</strong>
<div class='rolled'>
<$! this.htmlcontent.total || 0 $>
</div>

Something seems to be wrong with the above roll -- it failed verification.
</div>
<$ } $>
<$ if(window.is_gm) { $>
<div id="menu<$!this.id$>" class="flyout"/>
<$ } $>
</div>
</script>
<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_tokenroll" type="text/html">
<$ if(this.playerid == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
<div class='message rollresult you player-<$!this.playerid$>' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>' data-playerid='<$!this.playerid$>'>
<$ } else { $>
<div class='message rollresult player-<$!this.playerid$>' data-messageid='<$!this.id$>' data-playerid='<$!this.playerid$>'>
<$ } $>
<$ if(this.showname) { $><div class='spacer'></div><div class='avatar' aria-hidden='true'><$ if(this.avatar) { $><img src='<$!this.avatar$>' /><$ } $></div><span class='tstamp' aria-hidden='true'><$!this.timestamp$></span><span class='by'><$!this.who$>:</span><$ } $>
<div class='formula' style='margin-bottom: 3px;'>
rolling token
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
<div class='formula formattedformula'>
<div class="dicegrouping" data-groupindex="0">
(
<$ _.each(this.content.split("|"), function(rollimg) { $>
<div class="diceroll "><div class="dicon"><div class="didroll"><img draggable="false" src="<$!unescape(rollimg)$>"></div><div class="backing"></div></div></div>
<$ }); $>
)
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
<$ if(window.is_gm) { $>
<div id="menu<$!this.id$>" class="flyout"/>
<$ } $>
</div>
</script>
<script id="tmpl_chatmessage_error" type="text/html">

<$!this.content$>
</div>
</script>

<$!this.who$> <$=d20ext.dice_formatter.replaceInlineRolls(this.content, this, d20ext.utils.htmlAllowed + "<a>")$>

<script id="tmpl_joingame" type="text/html">

<a class='btn btn-primary createaccount' href='javascript:void(0);' style='color: white; font-size: 1.1em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;'>
Create an Account
</a>
</p>
<div style='float: right; margin-top: 5px;'><a class="tipme" style="cursor: help;" title="You need to create an account so we can keep track of your preferences, macros, and what characters are assigned to you between play sessions. We don't use your information for anything else.">Why do I need an account?</a></div>

<p class='instructions2' style='display: none;'>Fill out the form below to create a new Roll20 account.</a></p>

</div>
<label>Your Email</label>
<input class='email' type='text'>

<div class='clear'></div>
<div class='registerfield'>
<label>Confirm Password</label>
<input class='confirmpassword' type='password'>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
<p style='text-align: right;'>
<button class='btn btn-primary signin'>Sign In</button>
</p>
</form>
</div>
</div>

<script type="text/html" id="tmpl_hand">

	<div class="hand">

		<$ if(this.model.get("currentHand") != "") { $>
			<$ var othis = this; $>
			<$ _.each(this.model.currentPlayerVisibleCardBacks(), function(cardback) { $>
			<div class="cardback">
					<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(cardback.avatar)) { $>
						<video src="<$! cardback.avatar $>" autoplay muted loop />
					<$ } else { $>
						<img src="<$! cardback.avatar $>" draggable="false"/>
					<$ } $>
				<$ if(cardback.shownum) { $>
					<span> <$! cardback.num $></span>
				<$ } $>
			</div>
			<$ }); $>
			<div class="handcontainer popover <$ if(this.showopen) { $>open" style="left: <$! this.oldoffset $>;<$ } $>" data-handid="<$!this.model.id$>">
				<div class="btn-group">
				  <button class="btn bycard <$ if(this.model.get("currentView") == "bycard") { $>active<$ } $>">All</button>
				  <button class="btn bydeck <$ if(this.model.get("currentView") == "bydeck") { $>active<$ } $>">By Deck</button>
				</div>
				<$ if(this.model.get("currentView") == "bycard") { $>
				<h2>All Cards in Hand</h2>
				<div class="cardgroup">
				<$ _.each(this.model.allCards(), function(card) { $>
					<$ if(!card.collection) { return true; } $>
					<$ var cardperms = othis.model.currentPlayerPermissions(card); $>
					<$ var cardAvatar = card.getAvatar(); $>
					<$ if(cardperms.seenum) { $>
					<div class="cardinhand" data-cardid="<$! card.id $>">
						<$ if(cardperms.seefronts) { $>
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(cardAvatar)) { $>
								<a href="<$! cardAvatar $>" class="lightly" draggable="false">
									<video src="<$! cardAvatar $>" autoplay muted loop />
								</a>
							<$ } else { $>
								<a href="<$!cardAvatar.replace('/med.', '/max.')$>" class="lightly" draggable="false">
									<img src="<$! cardAvatar $>" />
								</a>
							<$ } $>
						<$ } else { $>
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getBacking())) { $>
								<video src="<$! card.getBacking() $>" autoplay muted loop />
							<$ } else { $>
								<img src="<$! card.getBacking() $>" draggable="false" />
							<$ } $>
						<$ } $>
						<$ if(othis.model.get("type") == "playerhand" && othis.model.get("parentid") !== window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
							<div class="steal"><span>Steal Card</span></div>
						<$ } $>
						<$ if(othis.metaData[card.id] && othis.metaData[card.id]["bar1_value"]) { $>
							<div class='cardlabel'><span><$!  othis.metaData[card.id]["bar1_value"] $></span></div>
						<$ } $>
					</div>
					<$ } $>
				<$ }); $>
				<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<$ } else { $>
				<$ _.each(this.model.hasDeckIDs, function(deckid) { $>
					<$ var thisdeck = window.Campaign.decks.get(deckid); $>
					<$ if(!thisdeck) return true; $>
					<h2>
						<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(thisdeck.getAvatar())) { $>
							<video src="<$! thisdeck.getAvatar() $>" autoplay muted loop />
						<$ } else { $>
							<img src="<$!thisdeck.getAvatar()$>" />
						<$ } $>
						<$!thisdeck.get("name")$>
					</h2>
					<div class="cardgroup">
					<$ _.each(othis.model.cardsByDeck(deckid), function(card) { $>
					<$ if(!card.collection) { return true; } $>
					<$ var cardperms = othis.model.currentPlayerPermissions(card); $>
					<$ if(cardperms.seenum) { $>
					<div class="cardinhand" data-cardid="<$! card.id $>">
						<$ if(cardperms.seefronts) { $>
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getAvatar())) { $>
								<a href="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" class="lightly" draggable="false">		
									<video src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" autoplay muted loop />
								</a>
							<$ } else { $>
								<a href="<$!card.getAvatar().replace('/med.', '/max.')$>" class="lightly" draggable="false">
									<img src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" />
								</a>
							<$ } $>
						<$ } else { $>
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getBacking())) { $>
								<video src="<$! card.getBacking() $>" autoplay muted loop />
							<$ } else { $>
								<img src="<$! card.getBacking() $>" draggable="false" />
							<$ } $>
						<$ } $>
						<$ if(othis.model.get("type") == "playerhand" && othis.model.get("parentid") !== window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
							<div class="steal"><span>Steal Card</span></div>
						<$ } $>
						<$ if(othis.metaData[card.id] && othis.metaData[card.id]["bar1_value"]) { $>
							<div class='cardlabel'><span><$!  othis.metaData[card.id]["bar1_value"] $></span></div>
						<$ } $>
					</div>
					<$ } $>
					<$ }); $>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
					</div>
				<$ }); $>
				<$ } $>
			</div>
		<$ } $>
	</div>

</script>

<script type="text/html" id="tmpl_discardhand">
	<$ var othis = this; $>
	<$ if(this.model.discardmode === "choosefronts" || this.model.discardmode === "choosebacks") { $>
	<div class="hand deckpile" data-deckid="<$!this.model.id$>">

		<$ if(this.model.allCards.length > 0) { $>
			<div class="handcontainer open" data-deckid="<$!this.model.id$>">
				<div class="cardgroup">
				<$ var cardidx = 0; $>
				<$ _.each(this.model.allCards, function(card) { $>
					<$ if(!card.collection) { return true; } $>
					<div class="cardinhand" data-cardid="<$! card.id $>" <$ if(cardidx === 0) { $>data-resetdeckstack="true"<$ } $>>
						<$ if(othis.model.discardmode === "choosefronts") { $>
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getAvatar())) { $>
								<a href="<$!card.getAvatar()$>" class="lightly" draggable="false">
									<video src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" autoplay muted loop />
								</a>
							<$ } else { $>
								<a href="<$!card.getAvatar().replace('/med.', '/max.')$>" class="lightly" draggable="false">
									<img src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" />
								</a>
							<$ } $>
						<$ } else { $>
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getBacking())) { $>
								<video src="<$! card.getBacking() $>" autoplay muted loop />
							<$ } else { $>
								<img src="<$! card.getBacking() $>" draggable="false" />
							<$ } $>
						<$ } $>
						<div class="steal"><span>Drag to Deal</span></div>
					</div>
					<$ cardidx++; $>
				<$ }); $>
				<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		<$ } $>
	</div>
	<$ } else { $>
	<p>There are <$=this.model.allCards.length$> cards in the discard pile.</p>
	<$ if(this.model.allCards.length < 1) { $>
	<p class='alert alert-info'>There are currently no cards in the discard pile.</p>
	<$ } else { $>
	<p><button class='btn btn-primary drawnext'>Draw Card</button></p>
	<$ } $>
	<$ } $>

</script>

<script type="text/html" id="tmpl_cardtrade">

	<div class="cardtrade" data-cardtradeid="<$! this.model.id $>">

		<div class="row">
			<div class="span4">

				<h3 style="text-align: center;"><$! this.initiator.displayname $></h3>
				<div class="offering offering-initiator <$ if(this.initiator.id == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>dropzone<$ } $>">
					<$ _.each(this.model.cardsOf("initiator"), function(card) { $>
						<div class="offeredcard">
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getAvatar())) { $>
								<video src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" autoplay muted loop />
							<$ } else { $>
								<img src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" />
							<$ } $>
						</div>
					<$ }); $>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>

				<$ if(this.initiator.id == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
					<p>Drop Cards From Your Hands Above to Trade<p>
					<p>
						<$ if(this.model.get("initiator_accepts")) { $>
							<button class="btn btn-primary disabled" disabled="disabled">Trade Accepted</button>
						<$ } else { $>
							<button class="accepttrade btn btn-primary">Accept Trade</button>
						<$ } $>
						<button class="declinetrade btn btn-danger">Decline Trade</button>
					</p>
				<$ } else { $>
					<p>
					<$ if(this.model.get("initiator_accepts")) { $>
						<span class='pictos'>3</span> <$! this.initiator.displayname $> Accepts The Trade! Waiting on you...
					<$ } else { $>
						<$! this.initiator.displayname $> is undecided...
					<$ } $>
					</p>
				<$ } $>

			</div>

			<div class="span4" style="border-left: 1px solid #D1D1D1; padding-left: 15px;">
				<h3 style="text-align: center;"><$! this.receiver.displayname $></h3>

				<div class="offering offering-initiator <$ if(this.receiver.id == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>dropzone<$ } $>">
					<$ _.each(this.model.cardsOf("receiver"), function(card) { $>
						<div class="offeredcard">
							<$ if(/[\w\-]+\.webm/i.test(card.getAvatar())) { $>
								<video src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" autoplay muted loop />
							<$ } else { $>
								<img src="<$! card.getAvatar() $>" />
							<$ } $>
						</div>
					<$ }); $>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>

				<$ if(this.receiver.id == window.currentPlayer.id) { $>
					<p>Drop Cards From Your Hands Above to Trade<p>
					<p>
						<$ if(this.model.get("receiver_accepts")) { $>
							<button class="btn btn-primary disabled" disabled="disabled">Trade Accepted</button>
						<$ } else { $>
							<button class="accepttrade btn btn-primary">Accept Trade</button>
						<$ } $>
						<button class="declinetrade btn btn-danger">Decline Trade</button>
					</p>
				<$ } else { $>
					<p>
					<$ if(this.model.get("receiver_accepts")) { $>
						<span class='pictos'>3</span> <$! this.receiver.displayname $> Accepts The Trade! Waiting on you...
					<$ } else { $>
						<$! this.receiver.displayname $> is undecided...
					<$ } $>
					</p>
				<$ } $>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>

</script>

<script type="text/html" id="tmpl_stealrequest">

<div class="dialog" id="dicerollerdialog">

	<h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Basic Rolls</h3>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="basicroll" data-dice="d4"><span class="dfontd4 rolltype">d</span><br>d4</a>

<script type="text/html" id="tmpl_cs_attribute">
	<$ if(this.collection.character.currentPlayerControls()) { $>
	<div class="sortcontrols">
		<div class="handle fonticon-menu"></div>
		<div class="pictos deleteattr">*</div>
	</div>
	<$ } $>
	<div class='attrname'><$! this.get("name") $></div>
	<div class='current'>
		<$ if(this.collection.character.currentPlayerControls()) { $>
			<input type='text' value="<$!this.get("current")$>" name="<$!this.id$>-attrcurrent" />
		<$ } else { $>
			<span><$!this.get("current")$></span>
		<$ } $>
	</div>
	<div class='divider'>/</div>
	<div class='max'>
		<$ if(this.collection.character.currentPlayerControls()) { $>
			<input type='text' value="<$!this.get("max")$>" name="<$!this.id$>-attrmax" />
		<$ } else { $>
			<span><$!this.get("max")$></span>
		<$ } $>
	</div>
	<div style="clear: both; width: 100%; height: 1px; float: none;"></div>

</script>

<script type="text/html" id="tmpl_cs_ability">
	<div class="sortcontrols">
		<div class="pictos editabil">p</div>

		<div class="dfontd20 testabil">t</div>

	</div>
	<div class='heading'>
		<div class='abilname'><$!this.get("name")$></div>
		<div class='bartoggle'>
			<button class="rollabil btn dfontd20" title="Roll Ability">t</button>

				<input type='checkbox' value='1' class='showinmacrobar'>

			</label>
			<label class="istokenaction-label"><input type="checkbox" class="istokenaction" value='1' /> Show as Token Action</label>
		</div>
	</div>
	<textarea class='action tokenizer' style="width: 90%; min-height: 50px; margin-top: 5px;"></textarea>
	<small class='instructions'>Use <code>@</code> to insert Attributes, <code>#</code> for macros.</small>
	<div style="clear: both; height: 5px;"></div>


</script>
